PHOTO: Sudan Protest Started, Photo Update From the Protest. Please keep hashing to #SudanJan30 http://yfrog.com/gyji42j

@alunmcdonald:

 #SudanJan30 Universities seem to be the centre of protests, as usual. Reports of crowds at Omdurman Islamic, Khartoum &amp; Ahlia


